{"tid":891162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本 奇特啪啪啪經歷！有人返返吓工幫同事……","createTime":"2018-11-06T01:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T08:38:42.000Z","uid":25345,"like":24,"dislike":136,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"cd872637f21b8c5dd1093557771e1da6d81bc296","tid":891162,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:14:39.000Z","msg":"日本作為盛產愛情動作片嘅國家，唔知係咪佢哋對性方面都比較開放一點，今次就有日本網絡節目請來一班嘉賓大談性經驗！不過嘉賓竟然係一班「其貌不揚」嘅醜女，佢哋啲經驗認真奇特&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本網路節目最近請咗多位「醜女」討論性經驗方面嘅話題，其中一位藝人ぱいぱいでか美（PAIPAI DEKAMI）就自爆，竟然試過被全套《HUNTER&times;HUNTER 獵人》漫畫吸引咗去人哋屋企？<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/qjevnaablp6ar6y_4982400435bdcdfbf56650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fqjevnaablp6ar6y_4982400435bdcdfbf56650.jpg&h=44f09ea2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/qjevnaablp6ar6c_16283837675bdcdfc1e465f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fqjevnaablp6ar6c_16283837675bdcdfc1e465f.jpg&h=bdcf7cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢位女嘉賓就話自己係柏青哥店打工嗰陣，試過有人撩佢發生關係，結果佢哋就喺員工休息室度&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/qjevnaablp6ar6g_11469304855bdcdfc2e3e38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fqjevnaablp6ar6g_11469304855bdcdfc2e3e38.jpg&h=e8289886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢位女嘉賓就話自己同工作同事係「SP」關係。<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/qjevnaablp6ar6k_9596824655bdcdfc3e8789.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fqjevnaablp6ar6k_9596824655bdcdfc3e8789.jpg&h=524dd68e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲話會喺舖頭後面幫個男嘅用口&hellip;&hellip; 喂A片情節喎！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/qjevnaablp6ar6o_5947238355bdcdfc4ccb1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fqjevnaablp6ar6o_5947238355bdcdfc4ccb1b.jpg&h=f56de69b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢位女嘉賓仲誇張，話好鍾意同人喺地下停車場「開戰」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/qjevnaablp6ar6s_13166599345bdcdfc5dd169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fqjevnaablp6ar6s_13166599345bdcdfc5dd169.jpg&h=f569d50d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲要因為唔可以夜歸，所以都揀禮拜六日朝早10點「晨操」！<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/qjevnaablp6ar6w_17444393815bdcdfc6e2bfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fqjevnaablp6ar6w_17444393815bdcdfc6e2bfe.jpg&h=03cd840c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好以為呢啲好誇張，藝人ぱいぱいでか美（PAIPAI DEKAMI）仲搞笑，佢就試過竟然被人用全套《HUNTER&times;HUNTER 獵人》漫畫返屋企&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/qjevnaablp6ar6sx_4232354365bdcdfc848f4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fqjevnaablp6ar6sx_4232354365bdcdfc848f4e.jpg&h=96588093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n佢咁講：「有人問我要不要去他家看全套《全職獵人》，我就開心地去了」<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/qjevnaablp6ar6sy_3325185855bdcdfc96807a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fqjevnaablp6ar6sy_3325185855bdcdfc96807a.jpg&h=2f5d7d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過可能對方係毒L又或者太緊張，機會嚟到都唔識把握，佢睇完漫畫就走咗！"},{"pid":"563bf48cfc382003a32af893ab067d2a8c070f96","tid":891162,"uid":25345,"lik